      <title>中国称信心在政治局会议前恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/china-s-state-media-says-companies-can-overcome-challenges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国家媒体在高层经济决策者重要会议召开前表示，尽管面临国内需求疲软和激烈竞争等诸多不利因素，但中国企业的信心正在恢复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/china-s-state-media-says-companies-can-overcome-challenges</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 01:55:11 GMT</pubDate>
