    <item>
      <title>稀土精炼厂遭警告后 Iluka 股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/iluka-shares-slump-after-warning-on-its-rare-earths-refinery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利表示，尽管 Eneabba 稀土项目已从澳大利亚政府获得 4 亿澳元（2.58 亿美元）新资金，但该项目仍面临经济和执行风险。此后，Iluka Resources Ltd. 的股价一度下跌 10%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/iluka-shares-slump-after-warning-on-its-rare-earths-refinery</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 01:28:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
